(1)
Bryant Park, seen from the Bush Terminal Building west of
Sixth Avenue.

P. L. Sperr.

(2)
Bryant Park, seen from Sixth Avenue, four years later, during the reconstruction carried out under Park Commissioner Robert
Moses.

August 20, 1934.

P. L. Sperr.

(3)
The same as No. 1 from a lower view point and showing from left to right across the skyline the upper portions of Chanin, Lincoln, Lefcourt Colonial and the 10 East 40th Street Buildings.
August 19, 1930.

P. L. Sperr.
